Modifications in this fork:
  - Replaced Google Gemini API integration with AWS Bedrock (Anthropic
    Claude Sonnet 4.6) for text/reasoning agents.
  - Replaced the image-generation step with a deterministic Markdown
    "preliminary PaperBanana prompt" writer, so the pipeline produces a
    reviewable prompt document instead of a rendered image.
  - Added Bedrock client, prompt writer, and pytest unit/integration tests.
  - Removed Google-specific dependencies (google-genai, google-auth) and
    added boto3 for AWS SDK access.

